# GitOps Repository Code Owners
# These owners will be requested for review when someone opens a pull request

# Default owners for everything
* @platform-team

# ArgoCD configuration requires platform team review
/argocd/ @platform-team @sre-team

# Production overlays require additional approval
**/overlays/prod/ @platform-team @sre-team @security-team

# Platform components (LGTM stack)
/platform/ @platform-team @sre-team

# Business applications - each team owns their app
/apps/my-app/ @app-team @platform-team

# GitHub Actions workflows
/.github/ @platform-team @devops-team

